I noticed a few issues with CI right now that I have fixed here (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67542):
1. It looks like the recent move from TableList to TableGrid in FileList broke the results-table.spec.ts test. I'll unblock it for @Udit to fix sometime later
2. AppNav had a recent change that broke advanced-app.spec.ts. I fixed the boolean condition.
Thanks! Tomorrow is my designated fix all my cypress tests day
Alright that PR ironically kept failing CI, but https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67418 had it merged and that passed CI, so that merged with this PR's changes
